metadata.name: Coloured Chimp Society #1
metadata.description: The Coloured Chimp Society is a collection of 10,100 unique NFTs created by Coloured Lab - unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Coloured Chimp works as your Society membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits. The first of unlocked items will be the access to "THE SEEDING" area. It would be a collaborative area, where each members will be able to paint and sign your own Chimps. Also, there will be "THE FACTORY" area, where members will have discounts and priority to buy future NFT collection items created by Coloured Lab before the official launching. Random owners will win exclusive gifts and much more that will be revealed over time. Visit www.ColouredLab.com/nft/collections/coloured-chimp-society/ for more details.
